{"tid":1686055,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"記者採訪期間被捕, 警察拒表明身分及出示委任證","createTime":"2019-11-01T02:01:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T02:03:28.000Z","uid":264043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6158676ac79b525f1113df0c3bcd6db95d02b19d","tid":1686055,"uid":264043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T02:01:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZOMLJPw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZOMLJPw.png&h=68239afe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1393397810783930\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D1393397810783930&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvIv2J6e4EmGiVIqwvzORC%2Fw%3D&h=174e4ccc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1393397810783930</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rc5peRU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRc5peRU.png&h=597b4de7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HuhV5Yz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHuhV5Yz.png&h=2ef6a40e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據警察通例第20章- 第14條,<br />\n在與巿民接觸和行使<span style=\"color: red;\">警察權力</span>時，必須表明身分及出示委任證。在案發現場的便衣人員，須將委任證掛在顯眼的地方，讓人易於辨認其身分。<br />\n<br />\n除非：<br />\n(a) 情況不容許；或<br />\n(b) 出示委任證會影響警隊行動及／或危及有關人員的安全；或<br />\n(c) 要求不合理。 <br />\n<br />\n唔通個女記者被幾十個警察時，仍然可以影響行動，危及有關人員<br />\n既然警察拒絕出示證件，唔通記者拒絕出示記者證係好唔合理?"},{"pid":"bf3afd1ecb00cd2eaa6422fa0ae0a058a6953337","tid":1686055,"uid":264043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T02:03:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/pgo/tc/Cpgo020.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Finfo%2Fdoc%2Fpgo%2Ftc%2FCpgo020.pdf&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvIv2J6e4EmGiVIqwvzORC%2Fw%3D&h=f95152ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/pgo/tc/Cpgo020.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/11_useful_info/pgo.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Fppp_tc%2F11_useful_info%2Fpgo.html&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvIv2J6e4EmGiVIqwvzORC%2Fw%3D&h=991bebfa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/11_useful_info/pgo.html</a>"}]}